    "synopsis": "When Chaplain Elysius of the Salamanders is seized by raiding Dark Eldar, his captivity becomes far more than a single warrior's ordeal, for he carries secrets buried beneath Mount Deathfire that could mean salvation or damnation for Nocturne itself. The veteran warriors of the 1st Company, the famed Firedrakes, mount a desperate rescue, fighting their way into the corsair stronghold known as the Port of Anguish to wrest him from his tormentors. Meanwhile Dak'ir endures the brutal trials of Librarian training, and the visions that come to him hint at a darker future still. As old rivalries harden and the mysteries of the Tome of Fire deepen, the Salamanders are drawn ever closer to a reckoning.",
